# Curriculum & program docs

Parent: [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md)

## Tone

Direct, operational, no fluff. Each doc should state what's decided and what's still open.

## Voting model (keep aligned)

**Platform implements:** private 👍/👎 after written GitHub review per peer; winner = most 👍.

When editing governance/assessment docs, prefer updating stale ranked-choice language to match the platform (see `execution/marketing/site/content/program.ts`).

## Phase 1 projects

1. PM platform (cohort infrastructure)
2. Comms (replaces Discord)
3. Public showcase (hiring partners)
4. Unification (winners merge three)

## Phase 2

4. Learning app (≥25 users via Ludwitt/Hult API)
5. Venture (deck + production app)
6. Open source (≥1 merged PR; cursorboston.com, algorithmacy.org as starters)

